      <abstract id="aspace_98ecd6a37a4ab6867b3d27336b70856c">The <title xlink:type="simple" render="italic">Black Sun</title> Archive is a collection of correspondence and manuscripts sent to the poetry magazine, <title xlink:type="simple" render="italic">Black Sun</title> which was edited by poet, Harvey Tucker.</abstract>
